{
  "text": "Considering mentioned facts, Perception Neuron was selected. Developed by Noitom, this motion capture suit consists of individual sensors called Neurons. Each neuron houses an Inertial Measurement Unit with a accelerometer, gyroscope and magnetometer [CITATION_1] . This units should provide decent measurement values with reasonable price. Suit allows full body tracking. Noitom also provides a SW in the form of environment, where editing, real-time preview of animations and export to various formats are possible. The only limitations are warnings about wearing suit near the electric devices, which is not always possible in a factory.",
